      </div>

      <!-- Transport note -->
      <div class="alert alert-info">
        <strong>Getting around:</strong> Most activities are spread across the island. A scooter
        or minicar rental makes east-west coverage significantly easier. See the
        <a href="/Pilot.BM/visit/getting-around">Getting Around guide</a> for full transport options, or
        <a href="/Pilot.BM/directory">the directory</a> for tour operators and rental companies.
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
